'''埃莉諾·卡頓'''{{BD|1985年|10月24日|||}}是一名新西蘭的女作家。

==生平==
2013年憑長篇小說《[[發光體_(小說)|發光體]]》獲得2013年[[布克獎|布克獎]]，成為布克獎創立以來最年輕的得主，獲獎時只有27歲。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Christie |first1=Janet |title=Eleanor Catton on winning the Man Booker prize |url=https://www.scotsman.com/lifestyle/eleanor-catton-winning-man-booker-prize-1540387 |access-date=15 May 2020 |work=The Scotsman |date=6 April 2014 |archive-date=2020-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031142925/https://www.scotsman.com/lifestyle/eleanor-catton-winning-man-booker-prize-1540387 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

埃莉諾·卡頓於加拿大出生，她在美國出生的紐西蘭父親是一名研究生，在西安大略大學獲得博士學位。6歲時隨家人移居到紐西蘭，6歲時隨家人移居到紐西蘭，在約克郡的利茲（Leeds）住了一年，並在哪裡讀書學校。由於環境的艱難，她稱這種經歷開了她的眼界。大學於[[坎特伯雷大學|坎特伯雷大學]]就讀，碩士畢業於[[威靈頓維多利亞大學|威靈頓維多利亞大學]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thebookseller.com/profile/eleanor-catton-interview.html|work=The Bookseller|date=15 October 2013|last=Tivnan|first=Tom|title=Eleanor Catton Interview|access-date=17 October 2013|archive-date=2013-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131020155445/http://www.thebookseller.com/profile/eleanor-catton-interview.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=guardian>{{cite web|last=Cochrane|first=Kira|title=Eleanor Catton: 'I'm strongly influenced by box-set TV drama. At last the novel has found its screen equivalent'|url=https://www.theguardian.com/culture/2013/sep/07/eleanor-catton-interview|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|publisher=Guardian News and Media|access-date=19 September 2013|date=7 September 2013|archive-date=2020-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028205144/https://www.theguardian.com/culture/2013/sep/07/eleanor-catton-interview|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

埃莉諾·卡頓於2008年推出處女作《綵排》時已經獲得媒體的青睞，值得一提的是這也是她的碩士論文的題材<ref name=bookmunch>{{cite web|last=Clarkson|first=Annie|title='I am still astonished and a little bit suspicious that The Rehearsal has even been published' – An Interview with Eleanor Catton | Bookmunch|url=http://bookmunch.wordpress.com/2009/08/04/i-am-still-astonished-and-a-little-bit-suspicious-that-the-rehearsal-has-even-been-published-an-interview-with-eleanor-catton/|work=Bookmunch|access-date=19 September 2013|date=4 August 2009|archive-date=2013-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130912010034/http://bookmunch.wordpress.com/2009/08/04/i-am-still-astonished-and-a-little-bit-suspicious-that-the-rehearsal-has-even-been-published-an-interview-with-eleanor-catton/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 在那一年，卡頓獲得了愛荷華州作家工作室的研究金，在那裡她完成了文學碩士並教授創意寫作，直到2011年，她成為一名駐校作家。2013年的長篇小說[[發光體_(小說)|發光體]]更為她帶來首個布克獎。<ref name=bookmunch></ref>

==文學成就==
埃莉諾·卡頓於2008年推出處女作《綵排》這是她的碩士論文題材，該內容涉及到中學時男老師和女生之間的戀情。獲得媒體的青睞，那年，她獲得了愛荷華州作家工作室的研究金。<ref name=bookmunch>{{cite web|last=Clarkson|first=Annie|title='I am still astonished and a little bit suspicious that The Rehearsal has even been published' – An Interview with Eleanor Catton | Bookmunch|url=http://bookmunch.wordpress.com/2009/08/04/i-am-still-astonished-and-a-little-bit-suspicious-that-the-rehearsal-has-even-been-published-an-interview-with-eleanor-catton/|work=Bookmunch|access-date=19 September 2013|date=4 August 2009}}</ref> <ref name=brisbane>{{cite news|last=McEvoy|first=Mark|title=Interview: Eleanor Catton|url=http://www.brisbanetimes.com.au/entertainment/books/interview-eleanor-catton-20130912-2tl9e.html|work=[[Brisbane_Times|Brisbane Times]]|publisher=[[Fairfax_Media|Fairfax Media]]|access-date=19 September 2013|date=14 September 2013|archive-date=2020-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028210517/https://www.brisbanetimes.com.au/entertainment/books/interview-eleanor-catton-20130912-2tl9e.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2011年，她成為坎特伯雷大學駐校的作家，並進行編劇的工作，在2016年，埃莉諾·卡頓的處女作《綵排》被改編成電影，並在2016年多倫多國際電影節的“當代世界電影”放映了部分內容。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tiff.net/films/the-rehearsal/ |title=The Rehearsal [programme note] |publisher=TIFF |access-date=12 September 2016 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108090246/https://www.tiff.net/films/the-rehearsal/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.screendaily.com/festivals/toronto/toronto-unveils-city-to-city-world-cinema-masters-line-ups/5108484.article |title=Toronto unveils City To City, World Cinema, Masters line-ups |access-date=22 August 2016 |work=ScreenDaily |archive-date=2019-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191013092324/https://www.screendaily.com/festivals/toronto/toronto-unveils-city-to-city-world-cinema-masters-line-ups/5108484.article |dead-url=no }}</ref>

卡頓的第二本小說《發光體》於2013年出版。該小說入圍並因此獲得了2013年布克獎，這是有史以​​來最年輕的作家，以28歲贏得布克獎，是該獎有史以來最年輕的作家，此外《發光體》長達832頁，是其獎項在45年中最長的獲獎作品。<ref>{{cite web|last=Morris|first=Linda|title=Eleanor Catton youngest author ever shortlisted for Booker|url=http://www.theage.com.au/entertainment/books/eleanor-catton-youngest-author-ever-shortlisted-for-booker-20130911-2tjjm.html|work=[[The_Age|The Age]]|publisher=[[Fairfax_Media|Fairfax Media]]|access-date=19 September 2013|date=11 September 2013|archive-date=2015-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150825093112/http://www.theage.com.au/entertainment/books/eleanor-catton-youngest-author-ever-shortlisted-for-booker-20130911-2tjjm.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Masters">{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-24541612|title=Man Booker Prize: Eleanor Catton becomes youngest winner with The Luminaries|last=Masters|first=Tim|date=15 October 2013|work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|access-date=15 October 2013|archive-date=2021-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106080403/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-24541612|dead-url=no}}</ref> 評審團主席羅伯特·麥克法倫（Robert Macfarlane）表示：“這是一件令人眼花撩亂的作品。這是一件發光的作品。福伊爾斯（Foyles）的喬納森·魯賓（Jonathan Ruppin）說：“我相信她注定會成為這一代人中最重要，最有影響力的作家之一。” 

2013年11月，卡頓因其小說《夜光》而被授予加拿大總督文學獎。<ref>[http://www.3news.co.nz/Eleanor-Catton-honoured-with-Canadian-literary-award/tabid/418/articleID/321305/Default.aspx#.UoVnTOHIhnE Eleanor Catton honoured with Canadian literary award] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140813070051/http://www.3news.co.nz/Eleanor-Catton-honoured-with-Canadian-literary-award/tabid/418/articleID/321305/Default.aspx#.UoVnTOHIhnE |date=13 August 2014 }}. ''3 News NZ''. 15 November 2013.</ref>

2014年1月，惠靈頓維多利亞大學宣布授予卡頓就讀的文學博士榮譽學位，並且因提供文學服務而被任命為紐西蘭功勳勳章成員。<ref>{{cite web|date=18 March 2014|title=How Catton's life changed after Man Booker win|url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/entertainment/books/9841238/How-Cattons-life-changed-after-Man-Booker-win|url-status=no|website=Stuff|publisher=|access-date=2021-04-26|archive-date=2018-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181126033023/http://www.stuff.co.nz/entertainment/books/9841238/How-Cattons-life-changed-after-Man-Booker-win}}</ref>

隨後，TVNZ和BBC第二頻道將《[[發光體_(迷你劇)|發光題]]》改編成電視小型電視連續劇，於2020年5月17日首播。卡頓還擔任該劇的編劇。<ref>{{cite news |title=First-look image of Eva Green in BBC Two's The Luminaries |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/mediacentre/latestnews/2019/eva-green-the-luminaries |access-date=24 May 2020 |work=[[BBC_Two|BBC Two]] |date=21 March 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200509210215/https://www.bbc.co.uk/mediacentre/latestnews/2019/eva-green-the-luminaries |archive-date=9 May 2020}}</ref>

